      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine and transmission are functional but show significant wear, with noticeable fluid leaks and a rough idle that will require mechanical attention soon. The exterior has extensive body damage, including deep scratches, several large dents, and widespread paint oxidation, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and some non-functioning electronics. Please expect to invest time and resources into repairs to make this vehicle reliable for daily use.",
