    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a textbook example of JDM engineering excellence. Power is delivered by the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six, paired with the legendary Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. This collector-grade specimen remains in factory-stock configuration, featuring its original Torsen limited-slip differential and untouched double-wishbone suspension geometry. The chassis is pristine, retaining all factory VIN tags and a flawless finish. Mechanically sound with crisp shift gates and linear boost pressure, this vehicle offers a pure, unadulterated driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
