    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and the results are evident in every square inch. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from even the slightest swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, having been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating. All body panels align perfectly, and the factory-original wheels are entirely devoid of curb rash, wrapped in premium rubber with near-total tread depth remaining.\n\nStepping inside, you are greeted by the unmistakable scent of fresh, high-grade leather. The upholstery is taut and supple, with zero creasing on the bolsters or wear on the touchpoints. Every piece of interior trim, from the brushed aluminum accents to the digital displays, is flawless and functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one and remain plush and unstained.\n\nMechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. The engine bay is detailed to a professional standard, showing no signs of dust or fluid seepage. It has been serviced exclusively at certified intervals with a full paper trail included. On the road, the transmission shifts with seamless precision, and the suspension remains tight and silent. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
