      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been curated to an exacting standard, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver who demands absolute perfection. We invite professional inspection to confirm its pristine status.",
