      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a superlative iteration of the naturally aspirated S65 platform. The 4.0L V8 features individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential, the mechanical synchronization is flawless. This specimen is in showroom condition, featuring original paint depth and a chassis maintained with surgical precision. All critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been documented, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of this high-revving icon.",
